00:20:23,866 --> 00:20:31,034
reality that depending on how a developer might change either a certain mechanic or

311
00:20:32,376 --> 00:20:35,900
take away a skill from a certain character, that that might...

312
00:20:36,721 --> 00:20:44,164
ruin a professional eSports player career, either because they can't compete anymore

313
00:20:44,184 --> 00:20:47,106
or they just aren't as viable as another player.

314
00:20:47,186 --> 00:20:50,007
So I just want to know what is your thought on that.

